### WorkSupport360 API — REST Client test file
### Install "REST Client" extension in VS Code (humao.rest-client)
### Usage: Click "Send Request" above any ### block

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000
@adminToken = PASTE_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE
@freelancerToken = PASTE_FREELANCER_TOKEN_HERE
@clientToken = PASTE_CLIENT_TOKEN_HERE

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# AUTH
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### 1. Login as admin
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@worksupport360.com",
  "password": "Admin@123!"
}

### 2. Login as freelancer
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "rahul@example.com",
  "password": "Test@123!"
}

### 3. Login as client
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "john@abccorp.com",
  "password": "Test@123!"
}

### 4. Google Sign-In (replace with real token from frontend)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/google
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "idToken": "GOOGLE_ID_TOKEN_FROM_FRONTEND"
}

### 5. Register new client
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "newclient@company.com",
  "password": "Test@123!",
  "name": "New Client",
  "role": "client",
  "companyName": "New Company Ltd",
  "contactName": "New Client"
}

### 6. Register new freelancer
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "newfreelancer@example.com",
  "password": "Test@123!",
  "name": "New Dev",
  "role": "freelancer"
}

### 7. Refresh token
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "PASTE_REFRESH_TOKEN_HERE"
}

### 8. Get current user info
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 9. Logout
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer {{freelancerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "PASTE_REFRESH_TOKEN_HERE"
}

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# FREELANCERS (public + protected)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### 10. Search all freelancers (no auth needed)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/freelancers

### 11. Search by skill
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/freelancers?skill=React&isAvailable=true

### 12. Filter by max rate and country
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/freelancers?maxRate=40&currency=USD&country=India&page=1&pageSize=10

### 13. Get freelancer by ID (replace GUID)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/freelancers/FREELANCER_GUID_HERE

### 14. Get my private profile (freelancer)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/freelancers/me
Authorization: Bearer {{freelancerToken}}

### 15. Get my stats (freelancer)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/freelancers/me/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{freelancerToken}}

### 16. Update my profile (freelancer)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/freelancers/me
Authorization: Bearer {{freelancerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "aliasName": "Rahul S.",
  "currentRole": "Senior Full-Stack Engineer",
  "bio": "8 years building fintech and SaaS platforms. React + Node.js + AWS specialist.",
  "hourlyRate": 38,
  "currency": "USD",
  "country": "India",
  "timezone": "IST (UTC+5:30)",
  "skills": ["React", "Node.js", "AWS", "TypeScript", "PostgreSQL", "Docker"],
  "availability": [
    { "dayOfWeek": "monday",    "isAvailable": true,  "startTime": "18:00", "endTime": "22:00" },
    { "dayOfWeek": "tuesday",   "isAvailable": true,  "startTime": "18:00", "endTime": "22:00" },
    { "dayOfWeek": "wednesday", "isAvailable": false  },
    { "dayOfWeek": "thursday",  "isAvailable": true,  "startTime": "18:00", "endTime": "22:00" },
    { "dayOfWeek": "friday",    "isAvailable": true,  "startTime": "18:00", "endTime": "22:00" },
    { "dayOfWeek": "saturday",  "isAvailable": true,  "startTime": "10:00", "endTime": "18:00" },
    { "dayOfWeek": "sunday",    "isAvailable": false  }
  ]
}

### 17. Toggle availability
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/freelancers/me/availability
Authorization: Bearer {{freelancerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

true

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# REQUESTS
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### 18. List all requests (admin sees all)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/requests
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 19. Filter pending requests
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/requests?status=pending
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 20. Create request (client) — replace freelancerId GUID
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/requests
Authorization: Bearer {{clientToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "freelancerId": "FREELANCER_GUID_HERE",
  "sessionType": "demo",
  "preferredDateTime": "2025-07-15T19:00:00Z",
  "durationMinutes": 45,
  "budgetMin": 30,
  "budgetMax": 40,
  "currency": "USD",
  "description": "Need a React + AWS expert for a fintech dashboard. 3-month project, ~20 hrs/week."
}

### 21. Update request status (admin)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/requests/REQUEST_GUID_HERE/status
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "scheduled",
  "adminNotes": "Meeting scheduled for July 15 at 7 PM IST. Rate agreed: $35/hr."
}

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# MEETINGS
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### 22. List meetings
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/meetings
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 23. Schedule meeting (admin) — replace request GUID
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/meetings
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "requestId": "REQUEST_GUID_HERE",
  "scheduledAt": "2025-07-15T13:30:00Z",
  "durationMinutes": 45,
  "platform": "zoom",
  "meetingLink": "https://zoom.us/j/123456789",
  "agreedRate": 35,
  "currency": "USD"
}

### 24. Record meeting outcome (admin)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/meetings/MEETING_GUID_HERE/outcome
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "outcome": "approved",
  "notes": "Client happy with demo. Project to start July 20."
}

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# PROJECTS
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### 25. List projects (admin sees all)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/projects
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 26. My projects (client)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/projects
Authorization: Bearer {{clientToken}}

### 27. Create project (admin) — replace client + freelancer GUIDs
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/projects
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "E-commerce Recommendation Engine",
  "clientId": "CLIENT_GUID_HERE",
  "freelancerId": "FREELANCER_GUID_HERE",
  "description": "ML-powered product recommendation engine for XYZ Ltd",
  "skills": ["Python", "ML", "SQL", "FastAPI"],
  "hourlyRate": 2500,
  "currency": "INR",
  "estimatedHours": 80,
  "startDate": "2025-07-01T00:00:00Z",
  "endDate": "2025-08-31T00:00:00Z",
  "totalBudget": 200000,
  "milestones": [
    { "title": "Data pipeline setup", "description": "ETL + feature store", "dueDate": "2025-07-20T00:00:00Z", "amount": 60000 },
    { "title": "Model training", "description": "Train + evaluate model", "dueDate": "2025-08-10T00:00:00Z", "amount": 80000 },
    { "title": "API deployment", "description": "FastAPI + Docker", "dueDate": "2025-08-31T00:00:00Z", "amount": 60000 }
  ]
}

### 28. Update project progress (freelancer/admin)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/PROJECT_GUID_HERE/progress
Authorization: Bearer {{freelancerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "progress": 65,
  "status": "active"
}

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# TIMESHEETS
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### 29. List timesheets
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/timesheets
Authorization: Bearer {{freelancerToken}}

### 30. Submit weekly timesheet (freelancer)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/timesheets
Authorization: Bearer {{freelancerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "projectId": "PROJECT_GUID_HERE",
  "weekStart": "2025-07-14T00:00:00Z",
  "weekEnd": "2025-07-18T00:00:00Z",
  "entries": [
    { "date": "2025-07-14T00:00:00Z", "hours": 4, "description": "Auth module — JWT implementation" },
    { "date": "2025-07-15T00:00:00Z", "hours": 5, "description": "Dashboard UI — header + sidebar components" },
    { "date": "2025-07-16T00:00:00Z", "hours": 3, "description": "API integration — user endpoints" },
    { "date": "2025-07-17T00:00:00Z", "hours": 4, "description": "Bug fixes + code review" }
  ]
}

### 31. Approve timesheet (admin/client)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/timesheets/TIMESHEET_GUID_HERE/approve
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "approve": true
}

### 32. Reject timesheet with reason
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/timesheets/TIMESHEET_GUID_HERE/approve
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "approve": false,
  "reason": "Hours on July 16 appear too high. Please clarify the tasks."
}

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# INVOICES
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### 33. List invoices
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/invoices
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 34. Get specific invoice
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/invoices/INVOICE_GUID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 35. Mark invoice as paid (admin)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/invoices/INVOICE_GUID_HERE/mark-paid
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "invoiceId": "INVOICE_GUID_HERE",
  "method": "Bank Transfer",
  "transactionId": "TXN-20250715-8823"
}

### 36. Mark overdue invoices
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/invoices/mark-overdue
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# PAYMENTS
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### 37. List all payments (admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/payments
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 38. My payments (freelancer)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/payments
Authorization: Bearer {{freelancerToken}}

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# NOTIFICATIONS
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### 39. Get my notifications
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/notifications
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 40. Get unread only
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/notifications?unreadOnly=true
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 41. Mark one as read
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/notifications/NOTIF_GUID_HERE/read
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 42. Mark all as read
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/notifications/mark-all-read
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# STANDUPS
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### 43. Submit daily standup (freelancer)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/standups
Authorization: Bearer {{freelancerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "projectId": "PROJECT_GUID_HERE",
  "date": "2025-07-15T00:00:00Z",
  "yesterdayWork": "Completed auth module — JWT + refresh token implementation",
  "todayPlan": "Start dashboard UI header and sidebar components",
  "blockers": "Waiting for client to share brand color tokens",
  "hoursWorked": 4
}

### 44. Get standups for a project
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/standups/project/PROJECT_GUID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# REVIEWS
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### 45. Submit review (client)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/reviews
Authorization: Bearer {{clientToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "projectId": "PROJECT_GUID_HERE",
  "freelancerId": "FREELANCER_GUID_HERE",
  "rating": 5,
  "comment": "Rahul was exceptional — delivered ahead of schedule, communicated daily, zero issues."
}

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# ADMIN
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### 46. Platform stats (admin dashboard)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 47. Monthly leaderboard
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/leaderboard
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 48. Revenue report (last 12 months)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/reports/revenue
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 49. Promote user role (admin)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/users/USER_GUID_HERE/role
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

"freelancer"
